reviewText: Hilarious! We couldn't stop laughing!  Ken Kington is very funny!  Clean comedy!

My wife, son and I watched this together last night.  I haven't laughed so hard in quite a while.  I already have a copy; I was about to buy my sister a copy but it is out of stock. I confess Kenn's wife was my son's homeroom and language arts teacher.  Good clean fun.
